detail.name: Spy Robot
detail.effect: [Activate Main][Once per turn] Choose 3 cards from your opponent's hand and reveal them.

detail.name: スパイロボット
detail.effect: 【起動 メイン】【ターン1回】相手の手札3枚を選び、それらのカードを公開する。

faq.question: What does "choose 3 cards from your opponent's hand" mean, exactly?
faq.answer: You choose 3 cards from your opponent's hand without looking at the fronts of the cards (with the card information remaining hidden).

faq.question: What happens to the cards after being revealed by this skill?
faq.answer: After the cards are revealed, they are returned to a state where only your opponent can see their fronts (to a hidden state).

faq.question: 「相手の手札3枚を選び、」というのは具体的にどのように選びますか？
faq.answer: 自分から見えない状態で(非公開情報のまま)相手の手札を3枚選びます。

faq.question: このカードのスキルで公開したカードはその後どうなりますか？
faq.answer: 公開した後、相手にしか見えない状態に(非公開状態に)戻ります。
